        "question": "What types of programs does Teksversity offer?",
        "answer": "Teksversity offers a variety of online programs including undergraduate degrees (BBA, BCom), postgraduate degrees (MBA, MCA, MSc), and doctorate programs (PhD) across multiple disciplines such as business, technology, healthcare, and analytics."
