      {
        "question": "What is the duration of the online programs at Teksversity?",
        "answer": "Teksversity offers undergraduate programs that typically span 3 years and postgraduate programs that are structured as 2-year programs, designed to meet academic standards and evolving industry needs."
      },
      {
        "question": "What specializations are available in Teksversity's programs?",
        "answer": "Teksversity provides a wide range of specializations in business, technology, healthcare, analytics, and more, ensuring learners can align their education with current industry trends and career goals."
      },
      {
        "question": "Are the programs offered by Teksversity recognized and valid for career growth?",
        "answer": "Yes, all programs are delivered in collaboration with accredited academic institutions and are recognized for employment, further education, and career advancement across various sectors."
